These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: juice, hot-chocolate, milk, sprite
Pet: chinchilla, bird, ferret, goldfish
1. Pet:goldfish is on the left of Beverage:milk##1
2. Beverage:juice is on the left of Pet:bird##1
3. Beverage:sprite is in an odd position##4
4. Pet:ferret is on the left or right of Pet:goldfish##3
5. Beverage:juice is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | juice | hot-chocolate | sprite | milk |
| Pet        | chinchilla | bird   | goldfish | ferret    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: zombie, spy, sports, epic
Nationality: dutch, malaysian, pakistani, japanese
1. Movie-Genre:spy is on the left of Movie-Genre:epic##1
2. Nationality:dutch is on the left of Nationality:pakistani##1
3. Nationality:pakistani is in an odd position##4
4. Nationality:dutch == Movie-Genre:zombie##1
5. Nationality:malaysian is on the right of Nationality:pakistani##1
6. Nationality:dutch == Movie-Genre:zombie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | zombie  | spy  | epic |
| Nationality   | japanese    | dutch | pakistani | malaysian    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Food: broccoli, potato, kale, pear
Movie-Genre: zombie, drama, horror, mystery
1. Food:pear is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:mystery##3
2. Food:kale is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:mystery is on the left or right of Food:potato##3
4. Movie-Genre:mystery is on the right of Movie-Genre:horror##1
5. Movie-Genre:zombie is in an odd position##4
6. Food:potato is on the right of Food:kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | pear | kale | potato    | broccoli      |
| Movie-Genre   | horror        | mystery     | zombie | drama |

