.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
Hobby: filmmaking, skydiving, board-games, dancing
Music-Genre: punk, rock, country, dubstep
1. Hobby:skydiving is between Music-Genre:punk and Music-Genre:dubstep##2
2. Hobby:dancing is on the left of Hobby:filmmaking##1
3. Music-Genre:country is in an odd position##4
4. Music-Genre:rock is on the left of Music-Genre:dubstep##1
5. Music-Genre:rock is on the right of Hobby:filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | dancing | filmmaking | skydiving | board-games |
| Music-Genre   | country       | punk   | rock    | dubstep  |

