2. Nationality:argentine == Music-Genre:salsa##1
3. Nationality:german is on the right of Music-Genre:funk##1
4. Music-Genre:soul is on the far left##1
5. Music-Genre:indie is in an odd position##4
6. Nationality:chinese is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | soul  | funk    | indie   | salsa       |
| Nationality   | chinese | mexican | german | argentine |

