4. Job:musician is on the right of Pet:chinchilla##1
5. Job:paramedic is between Job:musician and Job:dressmaker##2
6. Pet:rabbit is in an odd position##4
7. Pet:rabbit is between Job:paramedic and Pet:mouse##2
8. Job:paramedic is on the left or right of Job:dressmaker##3

