2. Music-Genre:blues is on the right of Beverage:sprite##1
3. Music-Genre:soul is between Music-Genre:blues and Beverage:hot-chocolate##2
4. Beverage:sprite is in an odd position##4
5. Music-Genre:soul is on the left or right of Music-Genre:blues##3
6. Beverage:coffee is on the left or right of Music-Genre:rock##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | coffee       | hot-chocolate   | sprite | 7up |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | rock | soul        | blues    |

