2. Beverage:almond-milk is on the left or right of Beverage:hot-chocolate##3
3. Beverage:tea is on the far left or far right##3
4. Food:pear is on the left of Food:garlic##1
5. Food:garlic is on the right of Beverage:hot-chocolate##1
6. Food:pear is in an even position##4
7. Food:banana == Beverage:coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | tea | hot-chocolate    | almond-milk       | coffee |
| Food       | carrot  | pear | garlic | banana  |

